properties.Name: RelatedProduct
properties.Description: A relationship that exists between the related product during the associated period.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: RelatedProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: ProductRelationshipTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product Relationship Type.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date associated with the product relationship.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date associated with the product relationship.

Columns.Name: RelatedProductCostAmount
Columns.Description: The cost of the associated related product.

Columns.Name: DiscountPercentage
Columns.Description: The percentage discount for the product in conjunction with the related product.

Columns.Name: RelatedProductQuantity
Columns.Description: The quantity of related product required in the relationship with the product.

Columns.Name: RelatedProductIncludedNoChargeIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the related product at no charge.

Columns.Name: ProductWeighting
Columns.Description: The relative weighting of the product as compared to the related product.

Columns.Name: RelatedProductWeighting
Columns.Description: The relative weighting of the related product as compared to the product.

Columns.Name: ProductRelationshipNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the product relationship.
